      PskMessage.Header型の引数を持つ型を返すorg.interledger.pskのメソッド 
      修飾子とタイプ メソッドと説明
      List<PskMessage.Header> PskMessage.getPrivateHeaders()
      Returns a list of all private headers in the message, provided that either the message was not encrypted, or the private portion of the message has been decrypted by the receiver.
      List<PskMessage.Header> PskMessage.getPrivateHeaders(String headerName)
      Returns a list of all private headers in the message with the specified name.
      List<PskMessage.Header> PskMessage.getPublicHeaders()
      Returns a list of all public headers in the message.
      List<PskMessage.Header> PskMessage.getPublicHeaders(String headerName)
      Returns the all the public headers with the specified name.

      Adds a header to the private portion of the PSK message.

      Adds a header to the public portion of the PSK message.
      static PskNonceHeader PskNonceHeader.fromHeader(PskMessage.Header header)
      Constructs an instance of the header with the given header's value interpreted as a base64url encoded nonce.
